Package Service

Class UserService<T extends User,U extends BaseRepository>

Object
UserService<T,U>
Type Parameters:
T - the type of user managed by the service (e.g., Doctor, Patient).
U - the type of repository used by the service (e.g., DoctorRepository, PatientRepository).
All Implemented Interfaces:
IService<T,U>
Direct Known Subclasses:
AdministratorService, DoctorService, PatientService, PharmacistService
public abstract class UserService<T extends User,U extends BaseRepository> extends Object implements IService<T,U>
Abstract base class for user-specific services. Provides common operations for managing user information and integrates with a repository for data persistence.
